{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回「弯刀」承接上章忧愁谷之战。持四尺长剑的侏儒老人认出青青弯刀上的七字铭文，狂笑着出剑相逼。青青未及拔刀便被击落岩石，丁鹏不顾生死扑身挡剑，以血肉之躯替青青挨了致命一剑。青青在丁鹏倒下之际拔出弯刀反击，老人惨呼而退。\n\n丁鹏在幽谷中苏醒，发现自己身处华美宫室。青青的祖母——白发威严的老婆婆出现，坦言此处非人间，而是狐族居所。丁鹏得知青青一家皆为狐，却毫无悔意。老婆婆与青青的祖父（一位外貌近中年的青衣人）商议后，决定将青青许配给丁鹏，条件是他永远不得返回人间。丁鹏答应，获赠青青的弯刀为订礼。\n\n丁鹏在幽谷中安家，习得狐族刀法，三年已有小成。然而他夜夜噩梦，梦见亡父责骂他不孝无能，又梦见妻子一家化为狐群将他撕裂。他内心渴望出人头地、重返江湖。青青看穿他的心思，二人密谋趁七月十五祖父闭关之际逃离山谷。青青透露祖父虽神通广大却立誓永不离谷，祖母心软可用往事打动，八个忠仆则可用烈酒灌醉。故事在夫妻二人相依相守的誓言中结束。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "果然是这把刀，老天有眼，总算叫我找到了这把刀！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你还不拔刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "杀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "看来现在我已用不着忘忧草了，可是我觉得这样死更好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我从来也没有想到过，我死的时候，居然还有人为我流泪。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我真的在流泪？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "真的，你真的是在流泪，而且是在为我流泪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "不管怎么样，我总是为你而死的，你为我流泪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你没有死，也不会死了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为你已经死过一次，现在你既然已经到了这里，就不会再死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这里是我的家。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "这里只有你一个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这里连一个人都没有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "奶奶！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你应该知道这里连一个人都没有，因为我们都不是人，是狐。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你知不知道这地方本不是凡人应该来的？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "现在你已经来了，你不后悔？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我不后悔。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果我们要你留下来，你是不是愿意留下来？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我愿意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你真的已厌倦了人世？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我……我在外面，既没有亲人也没有朋友，就算我死在阴沟里，也不会有人替我收尸，更不会有人为我掉一滴眼泪。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你替青青挨了那一剑，也是心甘情愿的？",
      "tone": "柔和",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我当然是心甘情愿的，就算她现在要我替她死，我还是会去死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我也不知道是为了什么，我只知道，我死了之后，她至少还会为我流泪。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你已为他流过泪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是缘？还是孽？……这是缘？还是孽？……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "现在你已为她死过一次，她也为你流过了眼泪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "可是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你跟我来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "怎么样？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "text": "我也不知道应该怎么样，还是你做主吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我就知道你一定会把这种事推到我身上来！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "text": "我不往你身上推，往谁身上推？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "text": "你是青青的爷爷，又是一家之主，这种事本来就应该让你做主的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "现在你应该已经知道我们是狐，所以你在这里无论看见什么，都不必太惊奇。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为我们的确有点凡人梦想不到的神通！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我本来从未想到会把青青嫁给一个凡人，可是你既然已为她死过一次，她也为你流过泪。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你要知道，狐是从来不流泪的，狐的眼泪比血更珍贵，她会为你流泪，就表示她已对你动了真情，你能遇到她，也表示你们之间总是有缘。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "所以我也不愿意把你们这段情缘拆散。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "text": "你已经答应让青青嫁给他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我答应。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你做了我们的女婿后，虽然可以享受到很多凡人梦想不到的事，我们这里虽然一向自由自在，但是我们也有一条禁例！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果你做了我们的女婿，就绝不能再回到凡人的世界中去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "就因为我们知道你已厌倦了人世，所以才会收容你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "青衣人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "只要你答应永不违犯我们的禁例，现在你就是我们的女婿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_ren",
      "text": "我答应！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们也没有什么东西给你，这就算我们给你的订礼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "奶奶一定很喜欢你，所以才会把这把刀给你，你一定要特别珍惜！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai_ren",
      "text": "这把刀是绝对看不得的，看过这把刀的人，都已死在这把刀下。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你为什么不要这把刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "因为我要了也没有用！这把刀在我手里，简直和废铁一样。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "因为我根本不会使你们的刀法！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果你要学，我就把刀法教给你！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我梦见了我的父亲，他要用自己的一双手把我活活掐死。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他为什么要把你掐死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "他说我不孝，说我没出息！因为我已经把他老人家临终的遗言都忘得干干净净。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "其实你没有忘！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我没有！其实我时时刻刻都记在心里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他老人家临终时要你做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "要我出人头地，为他争口气！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我明白你的意思！我早就知道，迟早总有一天你要走的，你绝对不会在这里过一辈子，这种日子你迟早总有一天会过不下去！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "只可惜我也知道你的爷爷和奶奶绝不会让我走！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你是不是想一个人走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我当然要带你走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你肯带我走？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我们已经是夫妻，不管我到哪里去，都会带着你的！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你说的是真话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "当然是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果你真的要走，我们就一起走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "怎么走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我会想法子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "只要你对我是真心的，就算要我为你死，我也愿意。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他老人家的神通，除了大罗金仙外，天上地下，绝没有任何人能比得上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你的刀法在他老人家面前，连一招都使不出来的，他只要一伸手，你就倒下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "所以我们如果要走，就一定要趁他不在的时候溜走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "他好像从来就没有出去过！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "可是每年七月十五那天晚上，他都会把自己关在他自己的那间小房里，那几个时辰里，无论外面发生了什么事，他都不会管的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "可是他知道我们走了之后，还是会追。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "绝不会！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为他老人家已经立下重誓，绝不走出这山谷一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你奶奶好像也很不容易对付。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我倒有法子对付她。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "她老人家看起来虽然很严肃，其实心却比较软，而且……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你知不知道我的父母是怎么会去世的？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你父亲不肯带她走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我父亲虽然答应了她，我爷爷和我奶奶却坚决不肯，他们走了两次，都没有走成，所以我母亲……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这件事我奶奶虽然从来不提，可是我知道她心里一定很难受，到了万不得已时，我只要提起这件事，她一定会让我们走的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "这么样看来，我们一定有希望！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "可是我们也有问题，最少还有八个问题。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "八个问题？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不多不少，正好是八个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "难道他们也很不好对付？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你千万不要看轻他们，就算他们没有我爷爷那种神通，只凭他们的武功，如果到人世间去也绝对是江湖中的顶尖高手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我知道江湖中有很多成名的侠士和剑客，我也看过几个，却没有一个能比得上他们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你看见过谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你说的红梅和墨竹，我就全都看见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "这两人也比不上他们？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他们之中无论哪一个，都可以在十招之内将这两人击败。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "幸好每年七月十五那一天，他们都会喝很多酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "会不会喝醉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "有时醉，有时不醉，他们的酒量都非常好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "可是我恰巧知道有种酒，不管酒量多好的人喝下去，都非醉不可。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 707
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你也恰巧能找得到这种酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我能找得到。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "今天是什么日子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "六月三十。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "日子过得真快，想不到一转眼间，四年就已过去，想不到我又活了四年。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你还会活下去的，还不知要活多少个四年，因为我活着，你就不能死，你活着，我也不能死，有了你才有我，有了我就有你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 725
    }
  ],
